{"id": 1531, "genre": 1000, "title": "你有过哪些跨性别的消费？", "description": "其实很多产品本质上都是 genderless 的，有时候区分男女还让购买变得麻烦了起来，所以，你都抢过你对象的什么东西用？（题图来自：Jeff Östberg）", "record_count": 17742, "comment_count": 88, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170222153904bRd2zBuC9c3Y5Kg8.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-23T17:00:44Z", "questions": [{"id": 1954, "title": "你有过哪些跨性别的消费？", "content": "你有过哪些跨性别的消费？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 170042, "content": "袜子，男袜比女袜颜色素净，图案也没那么傻", "image": "img/option/option/201702221431335LiUZuPINEaAQqpS.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170047, "content": "衬衫、T恤、羊绒衫，女款收腰不好看，穿男士的就能自由飞翔", "image": "img/option/option/20170222143937Mefw0tcNI57ABK4l.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170049, "content": "有些女装颜色姹紫嫣红，想买黑色就只能买男款", "image": "img/option/option/20170222144030UAvf19iD5hNrZRIQ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170050, "content": " 香水，大多数女香都是甜腻花香调，喜欢淡雅的柑橘调男香", "image": "img/option/option/201702221444411cHFRIiWpQZrL52y.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170059, "content": "背包、钱包，男士的颜色深耐脏，用起来也更结实", "image": "img/option/option/201702221526585Q7WHLE0zVqsg3dn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170060, "content": "脚太小的男士总买不到鞋，会挑中性一点的女款运动鞋买", "image": "img/option/option/20170222153006ostQkP0NOv6VGEcd.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170063, "content": " 洗面奶，男士洁面强调清凉控油，可干皮用起来脸疼，不如用女士的", "image": "img/option/option/201702221532153ez4gRjs8aOmCAP0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170068, "content": "护手霜、沐浴露，男士产品清一色古龙香，男士就不能用水果味？", "image": "img/option/option/20170222153508Talh45MW9nf7J2bx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170321, "content": "只有薄荷味才man？我就喜欢抢对象草莓味小零食吃", "image": "img/option/option/20170223112317Bt0DnCoP7K1YIwjA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 170328, "content": "新款科技产品，借口送对象买回来，再强行占用", "image": "img/option/option/20170223112747Uq03T7X14htFSoRf.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}